personalInfo.clubAffl: Skukuza GC (Kruger National Park, Skukuza, Mpumalange, South Africa)

tourBios.carHigh: 2013: Held the 36-hole lead before finishing T5 at the Dakota Dunes Open...Made four cuts in five starts and finished 50th on the PGA TOUR Canada Order of Merit. 2009: Played in The Open Championship at Turnberry...Won the Vodacom Business on the Sunshine Tour.
tourBios.personal: Began playing golf at the age of 11 at Skukuza GC in the Kruger National Park, South Africa.

dyn.dynResults: His best finish on the PGA TOUR Canada was T5th in 2013 at the Dakota Dunes Open presented by SASKTEL.
dyn.dynStats: He ranks 41st in Scoring Average (Actual) on the PGA TOUR Canada.
